    "Key ideas:\n",
    "- `np.meshgrid` creates the $(t,x)$ grid\n",
    "- `dX = f(T, X)` evaluates the slope at every grid point\n",
    "- Arrows are **normalized** to equal length so large slopes don't dominate\n",
    "\n",
