    "::: {.callout-note}\n",
    "## Forensic Application\n",
    "A body at $37°C$ found in a $20°C$ room: two temperature readings at known times determine $h$, then the equation $T(t_{\\text{death}}) = 37°C$ recovers the time of death.\n",
