    "Piece-by-piece with **matching** at $t=2$:\n",
    "\n",
    "$$Q_1(t) = \\tfrac{1}{2}(1-e^{-2t}), \\quad 0\\leq t<2$$\n",
    "$$Q_2(t) = \\tfrac{1}{2}(1-e^{-4})\\,e^{-2(t-2)}, \\quad t\\geq 2$$"
